{"tid":1698563,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"以蛇蠓食蛇黎講，其實有隻 真。神獸 仲勁過蛇蠓。","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:05:58.000Z","uid":331173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b225785bc686f0f464b6dff55b7bc10c20d5a4de","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/etjwuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/etjwuS</a><br />\n講起神獸同蛇蠓。以蛇蠓食蛇黎講，其實有隻 <em>真。神獸</em> 仲勁過蛇蠓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SnurlWz4NdM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSnurlWz4NdM&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=bf4a20c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SnurlWz4NdM</a><br />\n根據祖利安口述，<span style=\"color: orange;\">大鵬金趐鳥</span>（唔知係咪港人口中嘅<em>金翅大鑊鳥</em>，我有D亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n係印度教中嘅 <span style=\"color: gold;\">garuda</span>，相傳佢展開雙翼係大過地球，佢最愛食龍，<br />\n次次開餐都當D龍係意粉咁食。後來D龍頂唔順，同佛陀（應該係指釋迦世尊）求救。佛陀就叫佢佢地守八關齋戒，有守齋嘅龍（唔殺生）就會隱形唔會俾金翅鳥發現。因此，<em>金翅鳥就有食惡龍嘅形象，因為佢只睇到惡龍，而俾佢食嘅龍全部都嚇到條蛇咁</em>。<br />\n不過後話係，後來所有龍都去守齋，有D仲成埋佛添，金翅島無得食，又同佛陀求救。佛陀教左佢輪迴之苦勸掂左佢，答應左，有佛師子嘅一日我嘅佛弟子都會供齋菜俾佢。因此流傳左 <span style=\"color: gold;\">施食法門</span>。<span style=\"color: violet;\">信不信由你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又諗起有條片。<br />\n係講<span style=\"color: gold;\">大鵬金趐鳥</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">心經簡林</span>，同埋<em>疑似上面嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">壓勝術</span></em>。<br />\n<em>片中解釋，其實心經簡林唔係好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係用心經包裝左嘅一D... 唔知乜野衰野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iV7u08agP0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiV7u08agP0U&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=9446f842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iV7u08agP0U</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">信不信由你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b3e6f75beea3ce881e651c9347f57b9c2c5ba0","tid":1698563,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"今日好似好多區都見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8addaffd0bc75257543c986c005586fbac7064a3","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5b3e6f75beea3ce881e651c9347f57b9c2c5ba0","tid":1698563,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"今日好似好多區都見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"見到乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8d1f666570690d0a4be806351ef77abf3a5ae2","tid":1698563,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8addaffd0bc75257543c986c005586fbac7064a3","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5b3e6f75beea3ce881e651c9347f57b9c2c5ba0","tid":1698563,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"今日好似好多區都見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"見到乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"記錯咗 記得好似話啲雲似火鳳凰 應該唔係你講嘅神獸"},{"pid":"21f37590d8c14594ba596d9cd28ef99e29837980","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"大鵬金翅鳥現身？香港多區驚現火鳳凰雲 網民：香港守護神！吉祥之兆（7/11/19）<br />\n<a href=\"https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/152697/大鵬金翅鳥現身-香港多區驚現火鳳凰雲-網民-香港守護神-吉祥之兆\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.pres