e":{"pid":"4df04dd2202fb2ddbc9570e086ef134d0ac9885e","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3269672b02f52ecb97221530a96e19a9e36497","tid":1698563,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"抹緊汗，咁既然咁多迷信嘅人又做乜唔正經信下護法神<br />\n走去信其他無謂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我都好多疑問，如<br />\n明明係印度教神獸又點解會STATION係香港。唔明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUsjRbMJ-20&amp;list=PLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUsjRbMJ-20%26list%3DPLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=f442d258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUsjRbMJ-20&amp;list=PLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ</a><br />\n求人不如求己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自問自答，金翅鳥的由來，唐代入華 1:00<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1:45 專門對付 龍 同 似虫 嘅野 （蛇？）</span><br />\n我唔知佢講乜野風水師2014死左（是否指害人果個？）<br />\n我只知我真係FEEL到2015 開始頭腦恢復清晰<br />\n密宗D野真係好難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"9:43 西藏苯教。根據WIKI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該係指 shamanism（係一種橫跨北方歐亞版塊嘅信仰）。後果佛教傳入西藏，苯教俾佛教眇，所以苯教僧人融入左西藏佛教中繼續修行。非常興幸佢地成為左佛子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，希望有心人不要攻擊傳教仕，特別係漢傳佛教嘅法師，<br />\n因為漢傳佛教係無流傳到有攻擊性嘅法門。<br />\n因為漢傳嘅佛教係近乎完全無攻擊性！<br />\n攻擊佢地同打醫生差唔多，因為你本人都唔知幾時需要救助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n害佢地同害自己差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632a439fca96d1a8a1a301ee6e6cb0e4beafa160","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlMBceNN4n0&amp;list=PLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ&amp;index=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAlMBceNN4n0%26list%3DPLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ%26index%3D2&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=6405752d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AlMBceNN4n0&amp;list=PLTtaN--Bnv5nj62XuqOjrNWDOYqZUMMRQ&amp;index=2</a><br />\n11:50 講得好呀，唔需要用鬼魂去做事，怨怨相報何時了，用人間嘅辦法去做事<br />\n正經人 confirm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有睇過佢其他片，佢講其他野無講得咁差，講到成個達哥咁<br />\nBTW 其實當我去講一D敏感話題果時，講野都係同佢差唔多咁差<br />\n（自問對自己口材非常自信 ）應該有D野唔俾人講某D話題。"},{"pid":"7e86ecad7a4ec386762cf2d8397b8a8dc5dd9aef","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"事實上港人真係成日講有關&quot;鳥&quot;嘅詞𠥔，可能真係有D&quot;感應&quot;<br />\nE。G。金翅大獲鳥（受困時），獅鳥（保護市民的），罷鷲（對付藍店）ETC<br />\n原來香港有隻真守護神獸叫.... 而且仲係專食龍蛇嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大鵬金翅鳥</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698563</a> 大家可以對應下佢嘅形象是否大家心中的形象<br />\n傳聞呢隻守護神獸大概係2003年開始受困，事實上，<br />\n果幾年真係變左&quot;金翅大獲鳥&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n可能D普通市民都感受到 <span style=\"color: orange;\">金翅鳥</span> 大鑊中<br />\n2014年解放之後，至今，開始出現較正面嘅，幫到手嘅形象出現<br />\n而且出現係大家心中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不要灰心<br />\n圖：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/amyArLV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/amyArLV</a>"},{"pid":"2a2bb735e4ebc3cea5a7372ad2f327311564f9b9","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"【蛇獴救港】香港真係有連登「護港神獸」 米埔專家「行開行埋都見到」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191112/60255199?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60255199%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=17e57949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60255199%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=c640420c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191112/60255199?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a><br />\n咁我覺得呢隻獴會好危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW祖利安呼籲唔好再信蛇獴救蛇，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人打不死精神係不死鳥精神</span></span>，唔係獴呀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5fa2nIz-Fs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl5fa2nIz-Fs&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=bac3dfae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5fa2nIz-Fs</a>"},{"pid":"e2d555dd806be23ed250f5d1e0ef8e2b6240daba","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"蛇獴 vs 大鵬金翅鳥<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722293</a>"},{"pid":"d4bc1202be5db49c8db22e28ae358200a083c996","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"佛教故事描述跟<br />\n印度源頭既描述完全不同"},{"pid":"81663776ea0ff871c553f9c3dc408d16943540d7","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4bc1202be5db49c8db22e28ae358200a083c996","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"佛教故事描述跟<br />\n印度源頭既描述完全不同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"雖然我都唔明，但係大鵬金趐鳥同佛陀係有段古 #1<br />\n你有冇睇內文㗎？<br />\n我唔係太信D咩天干地支同動物物種有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且亦無任何神獸同獴有關，佢只係一隻小動物。<br />\n食蛇（龍嘅倦屬）黎講，小動物邊夠金翅鳥勁。<br />\n<blockquote>相傳佢展開雙翼係大過地球，佢最愛食龍，<br />\n次次開餐都當D龍係意粉咁食。</blockquote><br />\n而蛇就係龍嘅倦屬。<br />\n金翅鳥係有經典記戴嘅金翅鳥心咒，獴係完全無記戴。<br />\n雖然我都無念金翅鳥心咒。但若然要信，不如信金翅鳥。<br />\n<br />\n其實宗教好多時都會同源，<br />\nE。G。象神都有係佛教經典有記戴，佛教名叫歡喜天。"},{"pid":"bdb7b6503ed34b960d703c0035f28f6505fb70de","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"大鵬金趐鳥 : 宗教<br />\n蛇獴 : 風水術數<br />\n兩種要用不同觀點分析<br />\n鬥風水陣, 我會選蛇獴<br />\n<br />\n大鵬金趐鳥係神獸<br />\n但真係唔明香港既歷史, 幾時開始跟佢有過互動??<br />\n用佢黎宣傳西藏佛教? 如果真係要研究大鵬金趐鳥,<br />\n一定要了解埋印度教(佛教源頭)"},{"pid":"800d37f0d9898b60449639516194de74729ee6f9","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb7b6503ed34b960d703c0035f28f6505fb70de","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"大鵬金趐鳥 : 宗教<br />\n蛇獴 : 風水術數<br />\n兩種要用不同觀點分析<br />\n鬥風水陣, 我會選蛇獴<br />\n<br />\n大鵬金趐鳥係神獸<br />\n但真係唔明香港既歷史, 幾時開始跟佢有過互動??<br />\n用佢黎宣傳西藏佛教? 如果真係要研究大鵬金趐鳥,<br />\n一定要了解埋印度教(佛教源頭)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"術數神話同源啦-。-鬥無形力又邊會分開計。<br />\n人地經典記戴講到明金翅鳥係一隻大過地球神獸。<br />\n你唔係諗住囉D山山水水去擋下話？山精龍神都頂唔住啦（龍＝金翅鳥食糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n再者，你點知亥字去沖巳一定WIN。想沖毒蛇陣梗係用番金翅鳥啦，上面講左神話了。<br />\n係神話呀，唔係童話故事黎㗎。BTW，毒蛇陣幾年前已破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，古代係先有天干地支後有生肖，據我所知係D術家自己安上去㗎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講一點，術數＝天象，天象由天體形成，即係大概係計算緊天體之間嘅&quot;力&quot;<br />\n同埋以天體去量度時間，計算好時間再可能有D特別嘅ENCHANT。<br />\n所以術數同算術係唔同㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數字上單位上係咁樣表達唔代表無其他&quot;他力&quot;形響。<br />\n所以唔好太沉迷術數同算術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謙卑少少，人算不如天算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有神話點解唔用，搵隻小動物黎食D BB蛇把鬼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最低限度唔好囉食咁嘅野黎搶FO叫人唔好拜金翅鳥先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小D人供養喺咪會細力D？搵個差D嘅黎代替，分散D供養？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fd24530dad4ea33f6099ab12b16951358316ea","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb7b6503ed34b960d703c0035f28f6505fb70de","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"大鵬金趐鳥 : 宗教<br />\n蛇獴 : 風水術數<br />\n兩種要用不同觀點分析<br />\n鬥風水陣, 我會選蛇獴<br />\n<br />\n大鵬金趐鳥係神獸<br />\n但真係唔明香港既歷史, 幾時開始跟佢有過互動??<br />\n用佢黎宣傳西藏佛教? 如果真係要研究大鵬金趐鳥,<br />\n一定要了解埋印度教(佛教源頭)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但真係唔明香港既歷史, 幾時開始跟佢有過互動??</blockquote><br />\n你想佢黎佢咪黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係咁，你係香港人，又點解一定只可喺香港出現唔去得第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何況神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8602bb4f7890f71781569c77bdd6f2dc1fec89e","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fd24530dad4ea33f6099ab12b16951358316ea","tid":1698563,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb7b6503ed34b960d703c0035f28f6505fb70de","tid":1698563,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"大鵬金趐鳥 : 宗教<br />\n蛇獴 : 風水術數<br />\n兩種要用不同觀點分析<br />\n鬥風水陣, 我會選蛇獴<br />\n<br />\n大鵬